extends @views/layout/index.pug
include @views/mixins/code.pug

block variables
  - title = 'Templates - Frontend tooling ecosystem';

append style
  link(rel='stylesheet' href='./style.scss')

block content
  section.section.m-b-4
    .container(data-animate='fade-down' data-animate-delay='200')
      h1.title-h1.m-b-2.text-gradient-deep.text-center Templates
      p.title-h5.slate-500.text-center.m-b-4
        | Preconfigured project templates for different architectures and setups
      .description
        p.m-b-1
          | Templates provide a structured starting point for building frontend applications
          | using a modular tooling ecosystem with flexible architecture choices.
          | They are automatically selected by the CLI based on application type,
          | styling preprocessor, and scripting language, removing the need for manual configuration.
        p.m-b-1
          | Each template is preconfigured with build, runtime, and UI layers,
          | ensuring a consistent and production-ready setup out of the box.
          | SPA templates include full runtime integration with routing, reactivity,
          | and component lifecycle management for dynamic applications.
        p.m-b-1
          | MPA templates focus on simplicity and performance,
          | generating independent pages optimized for static content and SEO.
        p.m-b-1
          | All templates are fully standalone, meaning the generated project
          | can be extended, customized, and maintained without dependency on the CLI.
          | This approach allows developers to start quickly while retaining full control over project structure and tooling.

  section.section.m-b-4
    .container(data-animate='fade-up' data-animate-delay='200')
      h2.title-h2.m-b-3 Template Matrix

      .card.card--padding
        +code('text', 'Templates', false)
          | SPA  + SCSS + TS  → spa-pug-scss-ts
          | SPA  + SCSS + JS  → spa-pug-scss-js
          | SPA  + LESS + TS  → spa-pug-less-ts
          | SPA  + LESS + JS  → spa-pug-less-js
          |
          | MPA  + SCSS + TS  → mpa-pug-scss-ts
          | MPA  + SCSS + JS  → mpa-pug-scss-js
          | MPA  + LESS + TS  → mpa-pug-less-ts
          | MPA  + LESS + JS  → mpa-pug-less-js

  section.section.m-b-4
    .container(data-animate='fade-right' data-animate-delay='200')
      h2.title-h2.m-b-4 SPA Templates

      .card
        p.title-h5.m-b-2
          | SPA templates include full runtime integration with routing and reactivity.

        ul
          li DI container
          li SPA Router
          li Reactive state
          li Component lifecycle

  section.section.m-b-4
    .container(data-animate='fade-left' data-animate-delay='200')
      h2.title-h2.m-b-4 MPA Templates

      .card
        p.title-h5.m-b-2
          | MPA templates generate independent pages with webpack multi-entry setup.

        ul
          li No client-side routing
          li Static HTML output
          li Fast and lightweight
          li Ideal for SEO and landing pages

  section.section.m-b-4
    .container(data-animate='fade-up' data-animate-delay='200')
      h2.title-h2.m-b-4 Getting Started
      .card
        p.title-h5.m-b-2
          | To create a new project using the CLI, follow the quick start guide.

        a.link.btn.btn--outline.btn--medium(href='/cli.html')
          | Open CLI Guide
          svg.button-icon.icon--icon-small(role='img')
            use(xlink:href='#icon-arrow-next' href='#icon-arrow-next')
